data.description: Absolutely stunning! This Homes by Hesley residence boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, an office, and a spacious garage. Nestled in Saline County, you'll be conveniently situated just a short distance from both Bryant City Limits to the South and the Pulaski County line to the North. This exquisite custom-built home features premium finishes including Quartz Countertops, an Exterior Fireplace, Custom Cabinets, top-of-the-line flooring, and soaring ceilings throughout! The Master Suite boasts an exceptional layout, allowing seamless access from the bedroom to the Laundry Room without traversing the main living spaces. The property spans approximately 1.2 acres, showcasing meticulously manicured lawns cared for by Fairway Lawns since its installation in 2019. Plus, a generously sized driveway and a trailer parking area with a gravel base behind the fence gate. Benefit from Fiber Optic high-speed internet, Natural Gas, City Water, and the services of the Bryant Fire Department, offering a peaceful lifestyle without sacrificing accessibility. ***351k of the loan is assumable at 2.25% through Freedom Mortgage.***  ***Seller will take an offer price of $490,000 without assumable loan***
